metadata.description:
Meta Slides collection created by Fabeeo Breen.  
Shoes design is a combination between FBRN style and AI technology.  
Metaslide = Unique Rarity wearable - 1 owner only (Decentraland)  
Each minted NFT will generate its metaverse-ready version playable in different virtual worlds.  
  
In this experiment patterns has been generted with different AI tools to explore the combination of a new form digital of design, where human and machine works together to create something out of this world.  
Meta Slides is the perfect way to add a little bit of style to your virtual wardrobe. 

Fabeeo Breen is a Metaverse fashion brand exploring the intersection of fashion, design, and technology in virtual worlds.  
The brand's vision is to create a new landscape of fashion that is open, inclusive, and ever-evolving.  
FBRN is the symbol of a new fashion era.

Flex your experience with FBRN wearables in a variety of virtual environments: join discord server to find more.  
Metaverse is an expanding world, and we want our collectors to be able to express their unique style in any corner of it. 

NFT COLLECTORS BENEFITS:  
- FBRN wearables airdrops.  
- Metaverse integration.  
- Unique wearables (check traits for DCL rarity)  
- Virtual events.  
- Exclusive content available on discord server.  
- Future utilities.

FBRN Discord: https://discord.gg/ErKTmXQz6H
